title: The Killing of Freddie Gray – Episode 13 – Media
description:
June 5, 2017 / The public learned bout what happened to Freddie Gray from the Baltimore Sun and other outlets that promised exclusive information. They left out a lot of the real story.

Episode scoring music by AnimalWeapon, Blue Dot Sessions, Chris Zabriskie, Fleslit, H-LR, Jahzzar, Remain, Uncanny Valleys, VYVCH, and Sym5.
